Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Elasticsearch Query DSL 방식 검색
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/es/query-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "index": "transactions",
  "size": 20,
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "should": [
        {
          "match": {
            "txHash": "0x123"
          }
        },
        {
          "match": {
            "network": "ethereum"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "sort": [
    {
      "timestamp": {
        "order": "desc"
      }
    }
  ]
}

